Terminal 1: Start the Backend (FastAPI / Core Neural Engine)
This starts the backend memory manager, security layers, and LLM integrations.

bash
source venv/bin/activate && python app.py
Wait for it to say Application startup complete.

Terminal 2: Start the Frontend (Streamlit UI)
This starts the 10-theme multiverse UI and connects to your backend.

bash
source venv/bin/activate && streamlit run chat_ui.py